graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|manages RayCluster lifecycle| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0+<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|webhook certs| CertController[cert-controller<br/>v0.10.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes<br/>1.29+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Conditional)
    CodeFlare -.->|workload scheduling<br/>when AppWrapper enabled| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.8.3<br/>CONDITIONAL]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - OpenShift features)
    CodeFlare -.->|OAuth dashboard auth<br/>Routes<br/>enhanced security| OpenShift[OpenShift<br/>4.11+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|namespace discovery<br/>DSCInitialization CRD| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>INTERNAL]
    CodeFlare -.->|network policy ingress<br/>namespace location| KubeRayODH[KubeRay ODH Deployment<br/>INTERNAL]

    %% Integration Points - Outbound
    CodeFlare -->|API server calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    CodeFlare -->|metrics export| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>openshift-monitoring<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]

    %% Integration Points - Resources Created
    CodeFlare -->|creates & manages| RayResources[RayCluster Resources:<br/>- Pods deployments<br/>- Services<br/>- Routes/Ingress<br/>- NetworkPolicies<br/>- Secrets]
    CodeFlare -->|creates & manages<br/>when enabled| AppWrapperResources[AppWrapper Resources:<br/>- Kueue Workloads<br/>- Scheduled jobs]

    %% Components that integrate with CodeFlare
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI for RayCluster mgmt<br/>future integration| CodeFlare
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -->|Ray client connections<br/>ray.init| RayResources
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models<br/>future integration| CodeFlare

    %% External services created per RayCluster
    RayResources -->|OAuth proxy| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OpenShift only]
    RayResources -->|external access| OSRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>or K8s Ingress]

    %% Styling
    style CodeFlare fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External - Required
    style KubeRay fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Kubernetes fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External - Conditional/Optional
    style Kueue fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style OpenShift fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeRayODH fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSPipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Infrastructure/Services
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthServer fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSRouter fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Resources created
    style RayResources fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style AppWrapperResources fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
